4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The 16-week program includes three live online classes weekly, with a maximum of 16 participants. Students gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration and learn about cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp also covers risk management strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The course is available in English and Spanish. 

